5/19/2026 [Day - 1]
===================
1 AWARE - having knowledge of something, or being conscious of your surroundings, sensations, or a specific situation.
2 COLLECT - to bring, gather, or accumulate things together
3 DISCOVER - to find, learn, or become aware of something for the first time
4 ENGINE - a machine designed to convert energy (like heat from fuel, or electricity) into mechanical force and motion.
5 FORTUNATE - having or bringing good luck, success, or an advantage
6 IMAGINE - to form a mental picture or concept of something that is not physically present, has not happened yet, or is entirely abstract.
7 MISTAKE - an action, decision, or judgment that produces an unwanted, incorrect, or unintentional result.
8 SEVERAL - more than two but fewer than many.
9 SITUATION - the combination of circumstances, conditions, and events happening at a particular time and place.
10 WONDER - to feel curious about something, or to be amazed by something extraordinary.

